ass=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
